  "content": "<style>\n  .audio-gallery {\n    display: flex;\n    flex-direction: column;\n    gap: 20px;\n    padding: 20px;\n    max-width: 800px;\n    margin: auto;\n  }\n  .audio-item {\n    border: 1px solid #ddd;\n    border-radius: 8px;\n    padding: 20px;\n    box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n    background-color: #fff;\n    transition: transform 0.2s;\n  }\n  .audio-item:hover {\n    transform: translateY(-5px);\n  }\n  .audio-item h3 {\n    margin-top: 0;\n    color: #333;\n  }\n  .audio-item p {\n    color: #666;\n    line-height: 1.5;\n  }\n  .audio-controls {\n    margin-top: 15px;\n    width: 100%;\n  }\n  .audio-download-link {\n    display: inline-block;\n    margin-top: 15px;\n    font-size: 0.9em;\n    color: #007bff;\n    text-decoration: none;\n  }\n  .audio-download-link:hover {\n    text-decoration: underline;\n  }\n</style>\n\n<p>Listen to our selection of audio talks and guided sessions. You can add, remove, or update these from the admin editor.</p>\n\n<div class=\"audio-gallery\">\n\n  <!-- Audio 1 -->\n  <div class=\"audio-item\">\n    <h3>Guided Meditation for Stress Relief</h3>\n    <p>A 15-minute guided meditation to help you relax and de-stress. Find a quiet space and follow along.</p>\n    <audio controls class=\"audio-controls\">\n      <source src=\"/audio/guided-meditation.mp3\" type=\"audio/mpeg\">\n      Your browser does not support the audio element.\n    </audio>\n    <a href=\"/audio/guided-meditation.mp3\" class=\"audio-download-link\" download>Download Audio</a>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- Audio 2 -->\n  <div class=\"audio-item\">\n    <h3>Podcast: The Pillars of Health</h3>\n    <p>Episode 1 of our podcast discussing the fundamental pillars of a healthy lifestyle and the 7.4 theme.</p>\n    <audio controls class=\"audio-controls\">\n      <source src=\"/audio/pillars-of-health.mp3\" type=\"audio/mpeg\">\n      Your browser does not support the audio element.\n    </audio>\n    <a href=\"/audio/pillars-of-health.mp3\" class=\"audio-download-link\" download>Download Audio</a>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- \n  TEMPLATE: To add a new audio file, copy the block below and edit it. \n  You will need to upload your audio file (e.g., an .mp3) to the 'public/audio' folder first.\n  -->\n  <!--\n  <div class=\"audio-item\">\n    <h3>Your Audio Title Here</h3>\n    <p>Your brief audio description here.</p>\n    <audio controls class=\"audio-controls\">\n      <source src=\"/audio/your-file-name.mp3\" type=\"audio/mpeg\">\n      Your browser does not support the audio element.\n    </audio>\n    <a href=\"/audio/your-file-name.mp3\" class=\"audio-download-link\" download>Download Audio</a>\n  </div>\n  -->\n\n</div>"
